  "remarks": "\nFormer member of the State Duma and former Chair of the Duma Constitutional Law Committee. Responsible for facilitating the adoption of legislation on the annexation of Crimea and Sevastopol into the Russian Federation. Advisor to the Duma Speaker, Volodin. Former member of the Supreme Council of the United Russia party. The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
